INSERT INTO `present` VALUES ('SW-FZ-001', '电影拍板钟', '02', '020005', '222', null, '<p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; unicode-bidi: embed; direction: ltr; margin-bottom: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; language: zh-CN\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; language: zh-CN; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 0; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 估计不少朋友都有导演梦，这款导演</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 0; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">action</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; language: zh-CN; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 0; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">打板闹钟可以一圆你的梦咯。跳动的</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 0; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">led</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; language: zh-CN; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 0; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">数字仿佛把你带到了好莱坞大片的拍摄现场。定好时间，早上的时候打下板子，闹钟就停了，马上开始演绎自己一天的情景故事吧，发生什么故事，全在自己的导演，无论如何，打下板子的那一霎那，自己出演的这幕生活剧一定要演绎的精彩，让自己的人生不能平淡！</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; unicode-bidi: embed; direction: ltr; margin-bottom: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; language: zh-CN\"><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; language: zh-CN; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 0; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">注意事项